What does the following procedure return when called with the argument 5?

PROCEDURE mystery(n)
{
    result ← 1
    REPEAT n TIMES
    {
        result ← result * 2
    }
    RETURN(result)
}

What is the value of x after this code executes?

x ← 10
IF(x MOD 3 = 0)
{
    x ← x + 1
}
ELSE
{
    x ← x - 1
}
DISPLAY(x)
